The paper focuses on automating the process of discovering optimization methods for deep learning architectures using a Recurrent Neural Network controller trained with Reinforcement Learning. This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. Additionally, the paper specifically mentions the use of the method on image classification and neural machine translation, which are covered by cs.CV and cs.CL respectively. Finally, the paper also mentions the use of primitive functions such as the gradient, which falls under the category of neural networks and cs.NE.
